'''''Przegląd Tomistyczny: Filozofia - Teologia - Kultura Duchowa Średniowiecza''''' (''Thomistic Review: Philosophy - Theology - Spiritual Culture of the Middle Ages'') is a [[Poland|Polish]] [[Academic journal|journal]] published by [http://www.it.dominikanie.pl/en/ Instytut Tomistyczny] (Thomistic Institute) with its seat in the [[Dominican Order|Dominican]] [[priory]] in [[Warsaw]], [[Służew]]. This review publishes fruits of studies on intellectual and spiritual [[Christian tradition]] with a particular emphasis on Polish heritage, research on [[Middle Ages]], and philosophical and theological quest in the tradition of [[Thomism]].

This review was established in 1984 in continuity with ''Polski Przegląd Tomistyczny'' (''Polish Thomistic Review'') founded by Dominican Friars in January 1939. The calamities of [[World War II]] and crooked history of post-war Poland made this 75 years gap inevitable.

''Przegląd Tomistyczny'' prints original articles and [[book review]]s in [[Polish language|Polish]], [[English language|English]], [[French language|French]], [[German language|German]], and [[Italian language|Italian]]. It publishes also editions of short historical Latin texts as well as Polish translations of short source texts.

==External links==
* [http://www.it.dominikanie.pl/przeglad/ Website homepage] of ''Przegląd Tomistyczny''

